            <div class="title">
                European Recovery (Uk—Usa Agreement)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-06-29/debates/f59f67b4-7084-49a8-a7fa-c6d00e0eafdd/EmergencyPowersAct1920" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
